abstract: "This repository presents the Recursive Synthesis and Endogenous Bifurcation Dynamics Theorem, describing recursive inheritance of retained synthesis cycles, resonance-window phase transitions, endogenous bifurcation drift, attractor topology, retained operational domains, and qualitative characteristics of subsequent synthesis cycles in nonlinear open dissipative dynamic systems."
